Let me check.

319
00:25:22,083 --> 00:25:22,916
<i>I think…</i>

320
00:25:23,541 --> 00:25:26,000
<i>I'll never meet anyone quite like you…</i>

321
00:25:31,166 --> 00:25:33,583
<i>but I'll try to find someone even better.</i>

322
00:25:47,250 --> 00:25:48,708
<i>Thank you, Senpai.</i>

323
00:25:54,166 --> 00:25:58,291
