324
00:26:10,916 --> 00:26:13,541
SO YOU WENT TO HER PLACE
JUST TO TURN HER DOWN?

325
00:26:14,125 --> 00:26:15,041
YEAH.

326
00:26:16,500 --> 00:26:19,666
WHY DIDN'T YOU SAY SO IN THE FIRST PLACE?

327
