Take the opportunity.

344
00:28:29,958 --> 00:28:31,625
I just want to know.

345
00:28:36,083 --> 00:28:37,500
I'm not mad now.

346
00:28:37,583 --> 00:28:38,666
What for?

347
00:28:38,750 --> 00:28:39,875
You turned her down,

348
00:28:39,958 --> 00:28:41,250
and she accepted it.

349
